        {
            "title": "國際｜特朗普：伊朗軍事行動取得勝利  強調不容許擁有核武",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜特朗普：伊朗軍事行動取得勝利 強調不容許擁有核武\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜特朗普：伊朗軍事行動取得勝利 強調不容許擁有核武</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特朗普發表全國講話，交代伊朗軍行動最新發展，表示過去四周對伊朗的軍事行動取得快速、決定性、壓倒性勝利，宣稱伊朗已被遭受毁滅性打擊，強調絕不容許伊朗擁有核武。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9-%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E6%93%81%E6%9C%89%E6%A0%B8%E6%AD%A6-012128785.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 09:28:29",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
