        {
            "title": "富邦媒轉型智慧服務平台 3年內推動「AI購物助理」應用",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2YgTDjzi7SrGFrbm.GIpaQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/e9fd2ae3c574a8637649a0c836b082c7\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
